            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Measurements were corrected for the probability of",
                "proton tracks and track confusion counting of",
                "different energy ranges, different attenuation of the",
                "neutron flux when neutrons with different energies",
                "going through the emulsion, and the emulsion",
                "shrinkage. No correction is required for background",
                "neutrons because only the neutrons greater than 3 MeV",
                "are considered."
